Package: sNPDR
Title: Survival Nearest-Neighbor Projected Distance Regression
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Patrick", "Kampmeyer", email = "pak611@utulsa.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Bryan A.", "Dawkins", role = "aut"),
    person("Brett A.", "McKinney", role = "aut"))
Description: Feature selection for right-censored survival outcomes in
    high-dimensional data. Survival NPDR extends Nearest-Neighbor Projected
    Distance Regression (NPDR) to survival settings by regressing pairwise
    survival-time differences on pairwise attribute differences within a
    censor-aware nearest-neighbor neighborhood. Supports signed and absolute
    difference formulations, Kaplan-Meier imputation for censored neighbors,
    covariate adjustment, and elastic-net regularization. Includes ReGAIN for
    pairwise gene-gene interaction network reconstruction from survival data.
